<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="129">
The specific epithet &quot; 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="129">gladius</emphasis>
&quot; refers to the similarity in valve morphology contour with a sword.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
